{"tid":1200694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"十二號罷工罷課罷市 然後呢？","createTime":"2019-06-10T20:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T00:46:22.000Z","uid":101824,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29d0c0fc3214801e62317c9283d84e9947bcd794","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:44:32.000Z","msg":"雖然經歷完9號嘅事 係會失望<br />\n但係今日見到大家有進一步行動<br />\n罷工 罷課 遊擊 野餐等等 <br />\n相信都會重燃大家嘅希望<br />\n其實鬥爭只係啱啱開始<br />\n但係 十二號嘅行動 然後呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">然後咪要繼續落去囉</span><br />\n有冇人仲會咁傻咁天真<br />\n相信一日嘅行動就撤回修例呀？<br />\n最多咪推遲再推遲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以今次行動 係要[size=4]堅持 持續[/size=6]<br />\n你可能會屌 仆街 持續同不散有撚分別<br />\n但不散 已經成為我哋9號嘅失敗嘅最大原因<br />\n9號嘅活動失敗 係因為說好的不散 冇咗<br />\n令到真正相信不散嘅義士 咁樣比班狗侮辱<br />\n事實上任何抗爭都冇可能咁短時間做到<br />\n更何況我哋而家對住個痴撚線政府<br />\n<br />\n首先要記住 我哋今次嘅目標唔係推遲修例 <br />\n唔係林鄭下台<br />\n唔係李家超下台<br />\n而係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撤回修訂逃犯條例</span><br />\n林鄭 李家超下台 人人都想<br />\n但係要先記住今次一連串行動最基本最基本嘅目標 <br />\n連呢個目標都做唔到 又點樣令林鄭 李家超下台呀？<br />\n<br />\n所以希望我哋之後記住嘅6月12號 唔係單單一日嘅行動<br />\n而係各項抗爭活動嘅開始<br />\n希望各位 各界都做好心理準備 令各方面行動一路持續 直至撤回修例為止<br />\n而唔係12號一日之後 又各散東西<br />\n又比啲掌聲<br />\n我好希望留返所有掌聲 <br />\n比真係成功令到政府撤修例嘅各位 <br />\n無論再遊行又好 苦行又好 <br />\n野餐罷工罷課又好 <br />\n記得要持續落去 12號嘅野餐最多只係推遲<br />\n要長期抗爭 要贏 就要靠大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">堅持 持續</span>"},{"pid":"3e013f9a924597fae07e24ff80666b90d6008800","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:49:24.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e950418100a466fd3fa17cd26e648e23bddd6626","tid":1200694,"uid":233050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:50:57.000Z","msg":"同意，要有長期抗爭嘅準備<br />\n唔只係幾日，可能係幾星期，每個星期二、三咁<br />\n總之乜都有可能，乜嘢方法都可行"},{"pid":"8fa6a7d68e071d968d7caa1842132a8d24109bc1","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:57:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6c74a081ec24996e72c334e871a31ce1810ead2b","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:05:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"70b7dad61fe8d8550efeb0ddbbe7ddbc9f23714c","tid":1200694,"uid":95499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:08:14.000Z","msg":"越拖越耐咪盞搞到士氣低沉慢慢冇咗件事<br />\n要搞嘅就一鑊過搞大佢啦"},{"pid":"e67b3d20280f98df8d50427baebbb435bf98525b","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"70b7dad61fe8d8550efeb0ddbbe7ddbc9f23714c","tid":1200694,"uid":95499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:08:14.000Z","msg":"越拖越耐咪盞搞到士氣低沉慢慢冇咗件事<br />\n要搞嘅就一鑊過搞大佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:17:58.000Z","msg":"一鑊搞大佢只係適用頂住2讀<br />\n罷工罷課唔長期做又有咩用？"},{"pid":"a81ab6c0f9acd00951020d8f923f083004df2565","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:07:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"10d1f38b371dc680aa3fb5a2ddf1021ca6c1a60a","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:03:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3895e71f6cdb018b9bf781dfb6ff16406d79fe6","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c1cc56204b009f76b964f7bd7e7b10479597ae0","tid":1200694,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"ab9dd0764160036994dc633d24f374bbeb984d85","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"15de72046423afcb538df11d4e03f7593a5d6aec","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:32:04.000Z","msg":"自推一下<br />\n同埋經過今日班狗咁嘅行動<br />\n分開嚟講 雖然我地衝擊行動係失敗 <br />\n但國際會睇到警犬濫權 使用過分暴力嘅行為<br />\n其實我一直都好想國際幫手制裁香港<br />\n因為就衝擊 當啲狗打人打上腦嘅時候<br />\n我地嘅武力 資源完全不足 <br />\n制裁香港 令香港經濟轉差<br />\n再加上長期不合作運動<br />\n先可以撤回修訂逃犯條件"},{"pid":"cb60b9ccc28c5801c42f171e2d6c039e38c093ca","tid":1200694,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:33:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c0fd579806bc70d717aefed931a380e950e6ec2","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:41:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bd7ba9967f2546b037d9f41a1d5459d3732a6a2b","tid":1200694,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03ca6e1814ceef75b74cdcf19e6c7efbf0b361","tid":1200694,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:55:47.000Z","msg":"十三號馬照跑，舞照跳"},{"pid":"925443a2497af2b4dd6966643c0e78c7abffc4dc","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb03ca6e1814ceef75b74cdcf19e6c7efbf0b361","tid":1200694,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:55:47.000Z","msg":"十三號馬照跑，舞照跳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:59:44.000Z","msg":"激動啲問大家，到底你地諗住一日嘅罷工可以換到啲乜撚嘢返嚟？"},{"pid":"61613343fb63b878773df1bf0313a26016fcf6e7","tid":1200694,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"925443a2497af2b4dd6966643c0e78c7abffc4dc","tid":1200694,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb03ca6e1814ceef75b74cdcf19e6c7efbf0b361","tid":1200694,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:55:47.000Z","msg":"十三號馬照跑，舞照跳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:59:44.000Z","msg":"激動啲問大家，到底你地諗住一日嘅罷工可以換到啲乜撚嘢返嚟？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:03:04.000Z","msg":"我認為777最後會修改方案，由法院立法會把關<br />\n不過就唔會撤回"},{"pid":"68a908508